    "默认不保存。开启后每次截图都会按所选目录保存为 PNG。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Off by default. When on, each capture is saved as PNG to the chosen folder."
